Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.26,0:00:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gihon1进入预定轨道位置
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.59,0:00:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由空间位相雷达对质量进行再测定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.00,0:00:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,误差修正Plus0.03
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.86,0:00:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记录更新
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.91,0:00:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任务保持
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.75,0:00:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击队的情况呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.30,0:00:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突破第一宇宙速度
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.46,0:00:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即将到达攻击点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.19,0:00:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 马上就要开始哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.09,0:00:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我怎么破坏那块胆石
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.72,0:00:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是陨石
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.15,0:01:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是陨石才对 遥姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.05,0:01:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您可是任务的领队
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.75,0:01:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请有点领队的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.29,0:01:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱莉卡…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.90,0:01:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人感触很深啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.04,0:01:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到各国协同合作 向同一个目标努力时的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.59,0:01:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这正是拜学园长提供了加尔德罗贝的技术所赐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.94,0:01:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.86,0:01:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如说要感谢这座KARAGAU天文台在刚启动之后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.10,0:01:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶然探知到了那颗陨石呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果撞击到地面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.66,0:01:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅是艾亚利兹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.49,0:01:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周边6个国家都会全灭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.44,0:01:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.41,0:01:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吃团子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.02,0:01:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是贡品 现在还不行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.47,0:01:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星灭者离射出点还有10秒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.47,0:01:45.04,Note4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs80}{\pos(310,443)}Meteor Breaker
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.34,0:01:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Force Wing 抛离
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.97,0:02:01.74,Note4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs80}{\pos(431,440)}Meteo Breaker   Ignition
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.97,0:02:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星灭者 点火
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.72,0:02:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有碎石
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.47,0:02:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 会被大气层烧尽的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.54,0:02:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
