Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.96,0:02:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.70,0:02:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在Gihon1上检测出异常向量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.34,0:02:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏离轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.41,0:02:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星灭者进路修正
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.80,0:02:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来不及了 即将命中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.45,0:02:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未能直接命中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.92,0:02:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,残留有大块碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.56,0:03:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爆炸陨石再次加速
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.81,0:03:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突入大气层
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.93,0:03:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路线是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.82,0:03:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预计落下点是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.27,0:03:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风花市
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 追上去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 遥姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.12,0:03:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地面会有第二波攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.34,0:03:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痴情!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.34,0:03:15.47,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（日语中“地面”和“痴情”同音)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.53,0:03:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是地面 小遥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.11,0:03:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去试试
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白 认证拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.71,0:03:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许可
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.97,0:03:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍天!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.56,0:03:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meister爱莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.57,0:03:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激活Materialise Zwei
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追踪陨石中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.72,0:03:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Materialise Zwei?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.50,0:03:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meister爱莉卡的固有能力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我们也在调查中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.40,0:03:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先代苍天的青玉…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱莉卡也能使用她母亲的能力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:03:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.65,0:04:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到不如说那才是苍天之青玉本来的姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要保护好大家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.23,0:04:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.23,0:04:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拂晓!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍天之青玉…与Gihon1 正面冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.23,0:05:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是 爱莉卡·梦宫…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.24,0:05:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是 爱莉卡·梦宫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.48,0:05:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陨石成功击破
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.55,0:05:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mission Complete
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.82,0:05:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱莉卡…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.42,0:05:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保护好了哟 真白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.54,0:05:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.89,0:06:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.65,0:06:13.90,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}第一幕　梦的延续
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.25,0:06:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～哎～是梦!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.06,0:06:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底做了什么梦让你变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.39,0:06:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Miss玛利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.37,0:06:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.22,0:06:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Miss玛利亚 刚刚那是梦吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把陨石“彭”地一下……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.51,0:06:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.36,0:06:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是拯救这个星球的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.56,0:06:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}风花期报--小蚂蚁、拯救世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.03,0:06:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}先代苍天之青玉“雷娜”的亲生女儿 立下大功
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.60,0:06:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.94,0:06:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.31,0:06:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:06:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为了Meister但还不够学分的你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.96,0:07:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾还是我的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.22,0:07:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱莉卡·梦宫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.55,0:07:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去绕王宫跑五十圈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后把《乙女心经》从第12章到15章抄写一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～是～哎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.58,0:07:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.31,0:07:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.90,0:07:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.19,0:07:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meister爱莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.49,0:07:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对…打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 下一个议题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.74,0:07:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.83,0:07:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于下个月在阿尔泰领召开的SALT战略乙HiME限制公约
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.83,0:07:45.66,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（SALT:战略兵器限制交涉会谈）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.69,0:07:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 走吧 命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.17,0:08:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前略 尼娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.89,0:08:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给现在不知道在哪里的尼娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.49,0:08:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是一如既往的在心中给你写信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.64,0:08:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那以来已经过了一年
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.95,0:08:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城市已经恢复平静
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.21,0:08:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家每天都精神十足
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.81,0:08:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白最近非常的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.67,0:08:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得很有女王风范了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.17,0:08:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我现在基本上没能够帮上什么忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.16,0:08:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在正为成为一名出色的乙HiME努力学习中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.76,0:08:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候尼娜有心情的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.06,0:08:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请过来玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.84,0:08:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.22,0:08:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个国家一定能成为一个大家都能够笑容满面 快乐生活的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.16,0:08:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请快点解散! 解散!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.50,0:08:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在城门前抗议的行为是被禁止的!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是在行使劳动者的权利而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们见女王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.37,0:09:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.81,0:09:14.52,Note4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You的发明Now one push呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.81,0:09:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的发明又增加了一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.67,0:09:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教授 有关这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.53,0:09:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.69,0:09:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碎片落下形成的这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.11,0:09:24.25,Note4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为Unknown所以要Let's study OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.11,0:09:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不知道所以我们要来研究 OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.85,0:09:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《劳动者的最低酬劳取消法案》通过 是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.49,0:09:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风花市工会坚决进行罢工
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.06,0:09:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.13,0:09:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王的施政前途多灾多难呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.05,0:09:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,静留!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.47,0:09:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然好像遭到反对意见了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.22,0:09:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但考虑下风花的现状
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.06,0:09:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是适当的作法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.81,0:09:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.92,0:09:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下个月还有乙HiME限制的交涉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.19,0:09:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也是一样头疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.99,0:10:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学园长 样本回收完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.80,0:10:07.15,Note4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学园长 Return学园吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.80,0:10:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学园长 回学园吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.43,0:10:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研究员骑在教授背上算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.86,0:10:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托加尔老师也注意一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.31,0:10:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主任 就此结束 没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.36,0:10:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 再去一个地方好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.67,0:10:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 那个先放着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.82,0:10:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是确认一下痕迹就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话我这就去看看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.74,0:10:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏树就回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.30,0:10:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.71,0:10:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.18,0:10:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们保持对乙HiME战斗防御的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.18,0:10:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后退至加尔德罗贝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.51,0:10:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像普通那样回去不就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.87,0:10:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说总是这样 开会还真是累人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.81,0:11:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您做得很了不起 真白大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.58,0:11:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葵很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.81,0:11:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫门前静坐的那些人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家还不肯离去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.28,0:11:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.97,0:11:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.69,0:11:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 是这件事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.72,0:11:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.63,0:11:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能取消
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.09,0:11:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是必要的改革
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.90,0:11:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.15,0:11:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人说不定会降薪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.94,0:11:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 不会有那种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.64,0:11:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我是为什么整天参加这个会那个会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.20,0:11:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.55,0:11:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是大家都在担心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你难不成和那些抗议的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.57,0:11:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 谈过了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.43,0:11:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是笨蛋吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.20,0:11:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了“笨蛋”两个字了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.65,0:11:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么就不能听听他们的话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.85,0:11:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能随他们喜欢去做吗!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.63,0:11:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光靠怜悯是不能施政的!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.93,0:11:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白最近变了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.21,0:11:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你太一成不变了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.33,0:12:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟那边比起来样子完全不一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.32,0:12:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.79,0:12:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.35,0:12:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娇嫣的紫水晶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.58,0:12:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.92,0:12:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 一个人装大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.45,0:12:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶也说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,个子长高不代表长大了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.77,0:12:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱莉卡感觉像是受冷落而感到寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.71,0:12:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 不够坦率啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了不是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.20,0:12:58.06,Note4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh～This face very cute呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.20,0:12:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh～这张脸蛋很可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.20,0:13:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 今天也不知道一个人跑哪去了 真白她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.18,0:13:16.73,Note4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\c&H711AD6&}（警告：请不要给猫神大人投食 Meister舞衣）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.39,0:13:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 猫神大人是美食家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.81,0:13:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.41,0:13:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是猫神大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.68,0:13:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我合影
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.07,0:13:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 猫神大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.37,0:13:26.51,Note4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs80}{\fad(300,0)}黑之谷 改名为 国立公园 猫神山
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.49,0:13:31.55,Note4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（今天已被预定一小时）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.15,0:13:31.55,Note4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs80}猫神拉面本店
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.19,0:13:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 爱莉卡那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要知道我是下定了很大的决心才通过那个法案
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.02,0:13:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以吵架了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.66,0:13:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.30,0:13:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.20,0:13:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣 好想快点吃拉面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.76,0:13:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.39,0:13:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 用不着太钻牛角尖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.65,0:13:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白已经足够这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.17,0:13:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有钻牛角尖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.71,0:13:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 女王大人 猫神拉面一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.14,0:14:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好像很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫神大人的也很快就来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.96,0:14:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为很烫 要小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.89,0:14:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.08,0:14:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.87,0:14:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐～舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.49,0:14:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有关奴兽宿主解除武装的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.47,0:14:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加尔德罗贝那边也没有空闲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.15,0:14:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要全员解除有点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.94,0:14:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.54,0:14:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么小的孩子也持有奴兽 总觉得太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.35,0:14:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面会泡涨哟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.07,0:14:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.75,0:14:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是上次的陨石吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.98,0:14:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.01,0:14:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分析它的成分 调查它的组成
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.04,0:14:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有想知道的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.76,0:14:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.09,0:14:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是准将她们说过的神秘的轨道变更
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.26,0:14:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.85,0:14:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,静留她还没有回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.77,0:14:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有联络过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.13,0:14:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚 GEM通信或重粒子通信都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.09,0:15:01.82,Note4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是在途中Get pretty girl了～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.09,0:15:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是在途中遇到美眉了～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教授!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.23,0:15:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这就去联络
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.86,0:15:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 Meister维奥拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.45,0:15:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣 再来一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.54,0:15:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不是已经吃了很多了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.22,0:15:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会吃不下晚饭的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.65,0:15:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.30,0:16:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃饱了倒头就睡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.99,0:16:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.16,0:16:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也想睡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.52,0:16:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,静留姐姐现在的位置是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.62,0:16:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.81,0:16:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有GEM的反应呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.18,0:16:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.44,0:16:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也Nothing呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.82,0:16:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.47,0:16:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下 快到外面去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.47,0:16:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.15,0:16:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高次物质化反应
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.79,0:16:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好强大 这决不是舞斗服或是奴兽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.12,0:16:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 这是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.34,0:16:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey～大家Look
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.58,0:16:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奴兽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.66,0:17:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 这不是猫神公园的居住区中央吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.50,0:17:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在加尔德罗贝的记录上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.51,0:17:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是新型
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.76,0:17:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通报风华宫 主任
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.71,0:17:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱莉卡 我送你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.41,0:17:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.08,0:17:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迫水 调动风花军全军
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.55,0:17:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 向市民发出避难警报
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.77,0:17:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 爱莉卡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.42,0:17:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 快去找
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.61,0:17:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快醒醒 命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.94,0:17:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了 帮我认证
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.20,0:17:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meister舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.15,0:17:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也用奴兽迎战
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.88,0:17:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 战斗就交给乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.39,0:17:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.68,0:17:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把猫神大人带回山上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.79,0:17:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 祝您好运!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.81,0:17:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.32,0:17:47.51,Materialise,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\4c&H272FFE&}{\3c&H1A72DE&}Materialise!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.85,0:17:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到镇外去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.59,0:18:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meister舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.91,0:18:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Meister舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.39,0:18:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是悲剧的Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.07,0:18:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底要被叫到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.49,0:18:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.92,0:18:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去帮助观光客的避难
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.41,0:18:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要管我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.64,0:18:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只猫怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.02,0:18:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.71,0:18:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.19,0:18:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跑去哪里玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.61,0:18:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白才是 一个人偷偷跑到这里吃拉面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.55,0:18:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰唆 一开始还不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.95,0:18:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人都给我适可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.23,0:18:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是吵架的时候吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.15,0:18:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.35,0:18:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵架以后再吵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.65,0:18:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解放汝之力量 启动苍天之力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.37,0:18:46.78,Materialise,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\4c&H272FFE&}{\3c&HE58908&}Materialise!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.55,0:18:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小蚂蚁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.57,0:19:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 小蚂蚁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.55,0:19:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍天!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.96,0:19:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 爱莉卡
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HiME的音乐啊！！！！愕天王见参!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.09,0:19:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦哦 学园长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.02,0:19:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然也请求加尔德罗贝支援
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.22,0:19:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 好吧 帮你一把
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.52,0:19:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HE58908&}Load Chrome Cartridge
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.86,0:19:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.91,0:20:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是什么东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.49,0:20:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.65,0:20:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱莉卡的苍天之霹雳被破了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.69,0:20:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的家伙要怎么办好啊 主任
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.22,0:20:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.53,0:20:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是奴兽的话就该有奴兽宿主在才对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.22,0:20:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次又是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有入侵者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.02,0:20:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在乙HiME们的Grave Room里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.36,0:20:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 那是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.76,0:20:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入侵者夺走了真白的金刚石 正往真祖之间前进
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.28,0:20:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也正赶往那里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.64,0:20:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.35,0:21:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Materialise!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.91,0:21:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…真祖大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.16,0:21:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这里弄得一片狼籍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.59,0:21:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.10,0:21:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我现身
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.72,0:21:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.75,0:21:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳子老师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.31,0:21:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二三大人的反应正在加速下降
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.49,0:21:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么下去的话 学园长的认证会…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.74,0:21:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启动Emergency模式
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.32,0:21:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上把认证系统切换到那里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.55,0:22:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“那里”是?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.70,0:22:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.03,0:22:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,备用系统?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.03,0:22:04.46,Note4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Surrogate System?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.80,0:22:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Emergency模式
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.56,0:22:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.96,0:22:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认证系统被切换到备用的了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.66,0:22:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反省以前那种情况而制作的紧急备用系统
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.94,0:22:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主任 发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.10,0:22:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有入侵者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.30,0:22:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墓地传来了警报 真祖大人的反应消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.70,0:22:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去追踪的Miss玛利亚也失去联系
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.59,0:22:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上回来 学园长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.76,0:22:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真祖之棺有入侵者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.49,0:22:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.41,0:22:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学园长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.54,0:22:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学园长 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.29,0:22:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里没能及时逃离的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.58,0:22:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请去救那些人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.80,0:22:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学园长 回加尔德罗贝去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.26,0:22:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 真白 比起那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.38,0:22:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙HiME现在还是世界的中枢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.72,0:22:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再发生“那基”那件事就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.32,0:23:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.50,0:23:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱莉卡 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.07,0:23:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.79,0:23:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是约好了要创造让人们都能欢笑的国家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.78,0:23:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才在做身为王该做的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.63,0:23:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么就不明白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.55,0:23:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.38,0:23:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白的话就乖乖听从我的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.01,0:23:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.41,0:23:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把苍天之力量还给吾之乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.49,0:23:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给她
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.47,0:23:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 爱莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.07,0:23:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.94,0:23:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.35,0:23:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.45,0:23:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.17,0:24:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入侵者的位置呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.97,0:24:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.25,0:24:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那个 备用系统已经到极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.34,0:24:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.82,0:24:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概 只有一次有效
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.39,0:24:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.08,0:24:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不向真白求助
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.31,0:24:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了 爱莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.31,0:24:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.40,0:25:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.50,0:25:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣 爱莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.91,0:25:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真祖大人被什么人给破坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.76,0:25:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.77,0:25:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙夺走了被封印的真白的金刚石
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.05,0:25:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.04,0:25:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.31,0:25:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.74,0:25:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.39,0:25:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.59,0:25:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.06,0:25:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱莉卡!
